WEBVTT

01:51.400 --> 01:52.080
Well,

01:52.320 --> 01:54.520
come on. Let's toast to our fleeting youth

01:54.520 --> 01:55.880
and the end of the college entrance exam.

01:55.880 --> 01:57.560
Since the results will be out tomorrow,

01:57.560 --> 01:58.920
let's all have a drink together.

01:58.920 --> 02:00.180
Okay, come on. Cheers!

02:00.400 --> 02:00.880
Cheers!

02:01.280 --> 02:01.740
Cheers!

02:01.760 --> 02:04.200
Cheers!

02:04.320 --> 02:05.720
Cheers!

02:10.880 --> 02:13.080
The math questions in this year's exam were too difficult.

02:13.080 --> 02:14.600
I don't know how others did.

02:14.600 --> 02:15.320
Anyway,

02:15.480 --> 02:17.079
I'm ready to retake the exam.

02:18.040 --> 02:19.680
Didn't you throw away all your books?

02:19.680 --> 02:21.340
How are you going to retake it?

02:21.560 --> 02:22.120
Right.

02:23.240 --> 02:24.320
I was too hasty.

02:24.880 --> 02:26.200
Don't be discouraged.

02:26.280 --> 02:27.720
Maybe when the results come out tomorrow,

02:27.720 --> 02:29.250
you'll surprise everyone.

02:29.280 --> 02:29.960
Come on.

02:29.960 --> 02:31.680
Do you think everyone is Qingyun?

02:31.680 --> 02:32.610
With our scores,

02:32.640 --> 02:34.000
we should know where we stand.

02:34.000 --> 02:34.800
That's right.

02:34.840 --> 02:36.440
Will it kill you not to be sarcastic?

02:36.440 --> 02:38.700
Ruirui, why aren't you saying anything?

02:39.000 --> 02:41.040
You guys are having such a lively chat,

02:41.040 --> 02:42.370
I couldn't get a word in.

02:42.400 --> 02:44.840
Ruirui, didn't you estimate your score

02:44.880 --> 02:45.800
to be 610?

02:46.400 --> 02:48.800
But I'm not sure if my estimate is accurate.

02:49.280 --> 02:51.200
You guys can actually remember the answers?

02:51.200 --> 02:53.520
I can't even remember the ones I guessed.

02:57.360 --> 02:58.220
Class Monitor,

02:58.600 --> 03:00.000
aren't you going to study abroad?

03:00.000 --> 03:00.880
Can we ask you to buy things for us

03:00.880 --> 03:02.160
in the future?

03:03.080 --> 03:03.640
Okay.

03:04.080 --> 03:05.160
You're going to study abroad.

03:05.160 --> 03:06.280
Why didn't you tell me?

03:06.280 --> 03:07.880
Where are you going to study?

03:08.280 --> 03:09.640
I'm going to London.

03:09.840 --> 03:10.680
London.

03:10.760 --> 03:11.760
That's a big city.

03:12.000 --> 03:13.640
Then won't you be able to see Qingyun?

03:13.640 --> 03:14.920
Yeah.

03:17.520 --> 03:18.920
L-London is so big.

03:19.040 --> 03:20.840
I might not necessarily see him.

03:23.440 --> 03:24.240
What's wrong?

03:32.360 --> 03:33.880
Let's sing together.

03:33.960 --> 03:35.040
Let's sing.

04:44.320 --> 04:46.040
I miss him so much.

04:49.440 --> 04:50.280
I know.

04:51.080 --> 04:53.920
I really miss him.

04:56.480 --> 04:57.320
I know.

04:57.800 --> 05:00.000
I really want to tell him

05:00.680 --> 05:03.840
that I really like him.

05:06.520 --> 05:07.720
He will know.

05:09.480 --> 05:10.400
But,

05:12.560 --> 05:15.600
I will never see him again.

05:17.600 --> 05:19.880
Yuanbao, you still have me.

05:20.080 --> 05:20.680
I

05:21.120 --> 05:22.680
will always stay by your side

05:22.680 --> 05:23.610
and protect you.

05:24.040 --> 05:24.920
So,

05:26.200 --> 05:27.520
you are not alone.

05:28.360 --> 05:29.290
Don't be afraid.

05:44.840 --> 05:45.800
Mom, Dad,

05:46.360 --> 05:47.040
Grandma,

05:48.000 --> 05:49.930
I got into a university in Beijing.

05:51.320 --> 05:52.080
Grandma,

05:52.680 --> 05:54.360
I didn't let you down.

05:55.040 --> 05:57.360
It's a really good university.

05:59.000 --> 06:01.640
I'll be going to Beijing in a few days.

06:03.000 --> 06:05.680
I might not be able to visit you for a while.

06:06.480 --> 06:07.480
Don't worry.

06:08.360 --> 06:10.090
I will take good care of myself.

06:11.320 --> 06:12.040
Grandma,

06:14.280 --> 06:16.200
Please bless Mutou's family

06:16.800 --> 06:18.320
and keep them all safe.

06:31.120 --> 06:31.960
You're here.

06:33.560 --> 06:34.159
Ruirui.

06:36.280 --> 06:37.140
This is for you.

06:39.880 --> 06:41.760
What do you mean?

06:44.600 --> 06:45.320
Actually,

06:47.600 --> 06:49.000
I've thought it through.

06:50.840 --> 06:52.100
These things of yours,

06:52.800 --> 06:54.520
I wanted to give them back to you

06:54.520 --> 06:56.120
when we went to college together.

06:56.120 --> 06:57.040
But

06:59.000 --> 07:00.760
now I feel like we might

07:03.120 --> 07:04.650
not be right for each other.

07:06.440 --> 07:08.480
We are just good friends.

07:12.640 --> 07:15.480
What exactly are you trying to say?

07:17.200 --> 07:18.280
I just want to say,

07:18.720 --> 07:20.120
we are just good friends.

07:20.400 --> 07:22.130
Focus on your college studies,

07:22.400 --> 07:23.600
and don't wait for me.

07:24.960 --> 07:26.620
Here, take this as a souvenir.

07:57.840 --> 07:59.159
You pervert!

07:59.480 --> 08:01.140
Taking photos of me secretly.

08:03.960 --> 08:04.680
I'm sorry.

08:07.080 --> 08:09.740
You were the one who said you wanted to pursue me.

08:10.440 --> 08:12.960
Then you said we were not suitable.

08:13.360 --> 08:14.200
Why did you do this

08:14.200 --> 08:15.760
to me?

08:18.400 --> 08:22.260
I was afraid of affecting your college entrance examination before.

08:23.840 --> 08:26.570
But now you have received your admission letter.

08:28.440 --> 08:29.770
I have no more concerns.

08:30.240 --> 08:31.000
Anyway,

08:34.480 --> 08:37.720
you understand what I mean anyway.

08:41.520 --> 08:42.450
I'm leaving now.

08:45.880 --> 08:46.800
Stop.

08:55.560 --> 08:56.200
What?

08:56.960 --> 09:00.120
Afraid of holding me back because you didn't get into university,

09:00.120 --> 09:02.580
or do you think you're not good enough for me?

09:02.840 --> 09:04.520
Ruirui, you...

09:18.400 --> 09:20.920
Those photos you secretly took of me,

09:22.000 --> 09:24.000
If you really want to give them to me,

09:24.080 --> 09:25.680
bring them to me in Shanghai.

09:25.720 --> 09:27.920
I'll wait for you in Shanghai next year.

09:28.760 --> 09:30.920
If you don't get in next year,

09:31.520 --> 09:32.360
I'll...

09:34.000 --> 09:35.160
I'll kill you.

09:39.200 --> 09:40.160
What are you waiting for?

09:40.160 --> 09:41.520
Hurry back and study.

09:41.840 --> 09:43.500
Waiting for me to kick you out?

09:43.840 --> 09:44.840
Okay, okay.

09:44.920 --> 09:46.580
I... I'm going home right now.

09:48.840 --> 09:49.960
Ruirui, then...

09:50.240 --> 09:51.200
then wait for me.

09:58.040 --> 09:59.800
You must wait for me.

10:00.640 --> 10:02.080
Stop dawdling.

10:03.680 --> 10:04.640
Wait for me.

10:05.720 --> 10:07.160
Wait for me.

10:12.360 --> 10:13.440
How is she so smart?

10:13.640 --> 10:15.240
I can't hide anything from her.

10:15.240 --> 10:18.040
Ruirui, you must wait for me in Shanghai next year.

10:45.720 --> 10:46.440
Grandma.

10:48.400 --> 10:49.240
Mutou.

10:52.440 --> 10:53.440
I'm leaving.

11:07.400 --> 11:08.160
Yuanbao.

11:10.720 --> 11:11.320
Over here.

11:11.960 --> 11:14.090
Let's go to school. We're almost late.

11:14.120 --> 11:14.720
Let's go.

11:33.040 --> 11:34.960
Yuanbao, let's hurry.

11:35.560 --> 11:37.290
We're going to miss our flight.

11:49.160 --> 11:50.720
Let's go, Mutou.

11:51.520 --> 11:52.800
We're going to school.

12:07.240 --> 12:08.200
Thank you

12:08.680 --> 12:10.540
for giving me so many lucky stars.

12:11.200 --> 12:13.130
They brought me to where I am today.

12:15.040 --> 12:15.800
Auntie,

12:17.720 --> 12:19.040
after you leave,

12:19.640 --> 12:21.680
please help me pass these things

12:22.960 --> 12:23.960
to Mutou.

12:25.280 --> 12:28.120
I hope Mutou recovers and leaves the hospital soon.

12:28.120 --> 12:30.250
I hope Mutou doesn't get sick anymore.

12:30.880 --> 12:33.340
I hope Mutou's grades improve by ten places.

12:33.480 --> 12:35.920
If not ten, five is fine too.

12:36.680 --> 12:39.680
I hope Mutou finishes homework seriously from now on.

12:40.000 --> 12:42.200
I hope I can save enough allowance.

12:42.640 --> 12:45.400
give him an unforgettable New Year's gift.

12:46.120 --> 12:49.280
I hope Mutou will like the food I cooked.

12:49.640 --> 12:51.000
I hope Mutou and I

12:51.240 --> 12:54.170
can both get into universities in Beijing smoothly.

12:54.960 --> 12:56.320
I like Mutou.

12:56.840 --> 12:57.880
I hope

12:58.560 --> 13:00.040
he likes me too.

13:42.160 --> 13:45.440
Yuanbao, where on earth are you?

13:47.080 --> 13:47.760
Qingyun,

13:50.960 --> 13:52.280
I've been looking for you for so long.

13:52.280 --> 13:53.610
So you were hiding here.

13:54.200 --> 13:56.200
Let's go when you're ready.

13:56.400 --> 13:58.520
We can't be late for the class reunion.

13:58.520 --> 13:59.280
Tell me,

14:00.280 --> 14:01.400
will she see it?

14:01.600 --> 14:02.440
What?

14:04.520 --> 14:05.520
My work.

14:06.680 --> 14:07.760
Will she see it?

14:10.560 --> 14:12.690
All the heroines in your current works

14:13.600 --> 14:14.760
are named after her.

14:16.640 --> 14:17.560
And now you've won

14:17.560 --> 14:20.020
the Best International New Director Award.

14:21.200 --> 14:22.860
So she will definitely see it.

14:24.280 --> 14:26.010
But why hasn't she shown up yet?

14:36.800 --> 14:37.600
Qingyun,

14:39.240 --> 14:42.700
you've been looking for Yuanbao for so many years with no news.

14:43.440 --> 14:45.500
Are you really going to keep looking?

14:49.760 --> 14:53.280
Maybe she'll suddenly appear.

14:54.960 --> 14:56.090
So don't lose heart.

14:56.600 --> 14:57.520
Will she?

15:01.960 --> 15:03.200
Even if she doesn't,

15:05.280 --> 15:06.540
as long as you believe,

15:07.960 --> 15:09.620
you will definitely find her.

15:10.480 --> 15:12.880
Over the years, among the things you wanted to do,

15:12.880 --> 15:14.810
which one hasn't been successful?

15:15.760 --> 15:16.880
So this time,

15:17.480 --> 15:18.610
it will work out too.

15:20.720 --> 15:21.440
Yaqi,

15:23.120 --> 15:24.580
thanks for your hard work.

15:25.240 --> 15:26.120
Thank you.

15:27.600 --> 15:29.160
I never feel it's hard work.

15:30.240 --> 15:31.000
Besides,

15:32.120 --> 15:34.180
I don't need you to say thank you to me.

15:36.160 --> 15:37.760
If you have to say something,

15:39.320 --> 15:40.360
I hope

15:42.720 --> 15:44.380
it's those other three words.

16:00.080 --> 16:00.920
He's coming.

16:03.720 --> 16:04.480
Director Mu.

16:04.600 --> 16:05.480
Director Mu.

16:05.520 --> 16:06.400
Director Mu.

16:06.760 --> 16:07.560
Director Mu.

16:11.520 --> 16:13.120
Don't push. Okay.

16:13.880 --> 16:15.120
Everyone, step back a little.

16:15.120 --> 16:16.920
Thank you for your cooperation.

16:19.120 --> 16:21.920
Director Mu.

16:28.240 --> 16:28.880
Director Mu.

16:28.880 --> 16:30.720
Rumor has it that you're getting engaged to Miss Xing soon.

16:30.720 --> 16:31.600
Is it true?

16:32.040 --> 16:33.600
Director Mu, is what they say online true?

16:33.600 --> 16:34.680
When will the wedding be set?

16:34.680 --> 16:36.920
Director Mu, please say a few words to our fans.

16:36.920 --> 16:37.560
Director Mu, could you please

16:37.560 --> 16:39.360
say a few words to us? Director Mu.

16:39.360 --> 16:40.360
Director Mu.

16:40.360 --> 16:42.090
Director Mu, please look here.

16:43.480 --> 16:44.400
Director Mu.

16:44.800 --> 16:46.680
What about our exclusive interview next, Director Mu?

16:46.680 --> 16:47.360
Director Mu, don't go.

16:47.360 --> 16:48.280
Say a few words to us.

16:48.280 --> 16:49.540
Don't go. Director Mu.

16:49.760 --> 16:51.520
Director Mu, keep it up.

16:51.600 --> 16:53.960
Director Mu, please accept our exclusive interview.

16:53.960 --> 16:55.520
All right. Step back.

16:55.840 --> 16:57.000
Don't push.

16:57.960 --> 16:59.290
What's wrong, Qingyun?

17:01.240 --> 17:02.040
Nothing.

17:02.120 --> 17:04.520
Director Mu, please answer our questions.

17:25.000 --> 17:25.720
Everyone,

17:25.839 --> 17:28.520
as the initiator of this gathering,

17:28.680 --> 17:30.210
I'll propose a toast first.

17:30.800 --> 17:33.000
Today marks the 10th anniversary of our admission.

17:33.000 --> 17:33.880
We are also very honored

17:33.880 --> 17:36.160
to have invited a few of our teachers and classmates here.

17:36.160 --> 17:37.640
Here, I propose

17:37.760 --> 17:38.920
that we offer our first toast

17:38.920 --> 17:40.080
to our

17:40.120 --> 17:41.580
most respected teachers,

17:41.680 --> 17:43.920
wishing them good health and peace.

17:43.960 --> 17:44.440
How about that?

17:44.440 --> 17:45.160
Yes!

17:45.240 --> 17:46.240
Let's do it together.

17:46.240 --> 17:47.800
Come on.

17:49.160 --> 17:49.960
Come on, together.

17:49.960 --> 17:50.800
Cheers.

17:55.640 --> 17:56.880
Eat and drink well, everyone.

17:56.880 --> 17:59.320
I heard you recently opened another branch.

17:59.320 --> 18:00.960
You have two hotels now, right?

18:00.960 --> 18:03.680
You are a true tycoon now.

18:04.320 --> 18:05.160
What tycoon?

18:05.240 --> 18:06.960
I'm just a small restaurant owner.

18:06.960 --> 18:08.000
If we're talking about being impressive,

18:08.000 --> 18:10.060
it has to be Meng Jingu and Mu Qingyun.

18:10.120 --> 18:11.480
One is a great scientist,

18:11.480 --> 18:12.960
and the other is a famous director.

18:12.960 --> 18:14.490
Director Mu arrived today.

18:14.560 --> 18:16.320
The reporters and fans

18:16.320 --> 18:18.240
completely blocked my hotel.

18:20.560 --> 18:23.040
Today we have no great scientists

18:23.240 --> 18:24.360
or great directors.

18:24.360 --> 18:26.000
We are all classmates today.

18:26.160 --> 18:26.680
Right.

18:27.280 --> 18:29.210
We are all the same as ten years ago.

18:29.240 --> 18:30.360
Nothing has changed.

18:30.360 --> 18:31.840
Well said.

18:32.480 --> 18:33.960
The friendship between classmates

18:33.960 --> 18:35.360
is the purest.

18:35.640 --> 18:38.500
No matter how many years pass, it will never change.

18:38.840 --> 18:41.080
It's just that it's been too long.

18:41.200 --> 18:42.800
Some of the students' names,

18:43.040 --> 18:44.560
I can't even remember.

18:45.520 --> 18:46.760
You see, Mr. Tian's memory

18:46.760 --> 18:48.290
is getting worse and worse.

18:49.120 --> 18:50.080
Forgive him.

18:50.200 --> 18:52.560
His mind is full of Ms. Xu right now.

18:52.720 --> 18:53.520
Right?

18:54.120 --> 18:55.520
But seriously, guys.

18:55.840 --> 18:57.360
You've changed so much in ten years.

18:57.360 --> 18:59.560
I wouldn't recognize you on the street.

19:00.040 --> 19:01.000
Ruirui.

19:02.640 --> 19:03.920
When is the baby due?

19:04.080 --> 19:06.240
The due date is the 13th of next month.

19:06.440 --> 19:07.240
That's great!

19:07.240 --> 19:08.000
Ruirui.

19:08.240 --> 19:11.100
I didn't expect you to end up marrying Shang Ningyu.

19:11.320 --> 19:12.200
Don't mention it.

19:12.200 --> 19:13.440
Our love story

19:13.440 --> 19:14.680
has been quite bumpy.

19:15.120 --> 19:16.400
Tell us about it.

19:16.440 --> 19:17.240
Tell us.

19:17.240 --> 19:19.160
I've never heard you talk about it.

19:19.160 --> 19:21.600
As for me, you know my grades were pretty bad back in school.

19:21.600 --> 19:23.760
I failed the college entrance exam time and time again.

19:23.760 --> 19:25.560
So I went to Shanghai to make a living.

19:25.560 --> 19:27.400
I accompanied Ruirui while she studied,

19:27.400 --> 19:29.530
and opened a small restaurant myself.

19:29.560 --> 19:31.720
We've been through a lot of ups and downs

19:31.720 --> 19:33.200
to get to where we are today.

19:33.200 --> 19:35.330
So I am especially grateful to my wife.

19:35.560 --> 19:37.440
Not only did she discover my cooking skills,

19:37.440 --> 19:38.280
but every decision along the way,

19:38.280 --> 19:40.280
big or small, was made by her.

19:40.520 --> 19:41.920
If it weren't for Ruirui,

19:42.000 --> 19:43.680
I, Shang Ningyu, wouldn't be here today.

19:43.680 --> 19:46.880
So much time has passed in a flash.

19:47.160 --> 19:48.760
Our school days

19:49.000 --> 19:50.800
feel like just yesterday.

19:51.920 --> 19:52.980
Let's make a toast.

19:53.000 --> 19:53.520
Cheers.

19:53.520 --> 19:54.560
Come on.

19:54.800 --> 19:56.400
Come on, everyone together.

19:56.440 --> 19:57.480
Altogether.

19:57.680 --> 19:58.840
Bottoms up.

20:01.120 --> 20:02.400
Come, drink up.

20:06.080 --> 20:07.400
I'm so happy today.

20:08.160 --> 20:09.800
But since Yuanbao isn't here,

20:09.800 --> 20:11.800
it feels like something is missing.

20:12.120 --> 20:13.400
But I heard from my wife

20:13.400 --> 20:15.200
that she was supposed to come.

20:21.160 --> 20:21.720
Qingyun,

20:21.720 --> 20:23.040
I want to tell you something.

20:23.040 --> 20:24.120
Back in school,

20:25.080 --> 20:27.740
Yuanbao intentionally made me get close to her.

20:27.840 --> 20:28.600
The purpose

20:29.760 --> 20:31.560
was to make you go study in the UK.

20:36.760 --> 20:37.960
In college,

20:38.600 --> 20:39.800
we kept in touch a lot.

20:40.440 --> 20:41.640
After graduation,

20:42.680 --> 20:44.280
she moved to several cities,

20:44.880 --> 20:46.160
and we lost touch.

20:48.400 --> 20:50.440
You two were together in Beijing.

20:50.440 --> 20:52.960
I thought you would end up together.

20:53.520 --> 20:54.120
As for her,

20:54.560 --> 20:56.560
she always had someone in her heart,

20:56.920 --> 20:58.520
and no one could replace him.

20:59.040 --> 20:59.800
Qingyun.

21:00.720 --> 21:03.120
I heard that the class monitor

21:03.200 --> 21:04.800
has been with you all these years.

21:04.800 --> 21:06.400
So, you two...

21:06.880 --> 21:09.080
Our relationship is not what you think.

21:09.680 --> 21:10.760
Abao Pictures.

21:11.400 --> 21:12.560
Every production

21:13.040 --> 21:14.640
has a girl named Yuanbao.

21:15.320 --> 21:16.520
Who is on his mind?

21:16.760 --> 21:17.800
Don't you know?

21:18.760 --> 21:20.160
So devoted, bro.

21:20.720 --> 21:22.850
But you've been out of touch for years.

21:23.040 --> 21:25.760
What if she already has kids?

21:32.920 --> 21:34.050
Just left like that?

21:54.000 --> 21:55.360
You are too slow.

21:55.440 --> 21:56.300
Hold it steady.

23:27.600 --> 23:28.440
Slow down.

23:30.080 --> 23:31.080
Cover that up.

23:34.800 --> 23:35.480
Watch your hands.

23:35.480 --> 23:36.610
That's about right.

23:39.120 --> 23:40.120
Move the cabinet.

23:46.960 --> 23:47.480
Done.

23:57.880 --> 23:59.480
Are you looking for someone?

24:00.720 --> 24:03.250
Who told you to decorate this place like this?

24:03.360 --> 24:04.200
Who are you?

24:04.920 --> 24:06.980
I'm the previous owner of this house.

24:08.400 --> 24:11.200
These are our old furniture from over a decade ago.

24:15.040 --> 24:16.100
So it really is you.

24:37.600 --> 24:39.060
How do you have this photo?

24:39.600 --> 24:41.200
A Ms. Xiong

24:41.240 --> 24:42.300
bought this house,

24:42.920 --> 24:44.440
and asked us to follow this photo

24:44.440 --> 24:45.840
to decorate it like this.

24:52.120 --> 24:53.320
Yuanbao.

24:55.040 --> 24:56.400
Yuanbao.

25:05.000 --> 25:06.640
Do you know where she is now?

25:06.800 --> 25:09.200
She just left. She shouldn't have gone far.

26:09.920 --> 26:11.120
When did you get back?

26:12.480 --> 26:13.400
A few days ago.

26:16.080 --> 26:16.720
By the way.

26:17.160 --> 26:18.200
Congratulations

26:18.680 --> 26:20.210
on becoming a big director.

26:21.320 --> 26:22.450
I saw the video of you

26:23.800 --> 26:26.200
and Yaqi at the awards ceremony.

26:28.840 --> 26:29.800
She is

26:31.520 --> 26:32.580
really beautiful.

26:43.760 --> 26:44.640
You

26:46.040 --> 26:47.120
got married.

26:58.440 --> 26:59.500
Congratulations.

27:00.240 --> 27:01.120
Thanks.

27:02.320 --> 27:03.400
You...

27:04.800 --> 27:05.720
you go first.

27:07.800 --> 27:11.440
How have you been these past few years?

27:13.800 --> 27:14.600
Not bad.

27:15.800 --> 27:16.660
What about you?

27:17.880 --> 27:19.340
I'm doing pretty well too.

27:20.400 --> 27:22.660
The flowers in front of Grandma's grave,

27:23.400 --> 27:24.860
you put them there, right?

27:26.760 --> 27:28.690
I haven't been back for a long time.

27:29.080 --> 27:30.140
I should visit her.

27:31.320 --> 27:34.000
By the way, how are your mom and dad doing?

27:35.480 --> 27:36.610
They are doing well.

27:37.560 --> 27:38.880
Both have retired

27:39.440 --> 27:40.570
and gone traveling.

27:47.360 --> 27:48.440
Do you love him?

27:50.200 --> 27:53.480
I heard you organized a class reunion yesterday.

27:54.160 --> 27:56.120
Everyone must have changed a lot.

27:57.320 --> 27:58.360
Do you love him?

28:02.280 --> 28:05.600
I heard Qiao Yan had a baby.

28:06.560 --> 28:07.880
She's a mother now.

28:08.280 --> 28:10.320
Time really flies.

28:11.160 --> 28:12.000
So,

28:13.000 --> 28:14.000
do you love him?

28:19.600 --> 28:21.640
I have things to do, so I'll leave first.

28:21.640 --> 28:22.320
Goodbye.

28:40.800 --> 28:41.520
Come on.

28:44.080 --> 28:45.120
You are so bad.

28:45.240 --> 28:46.700
You are bullying me again.

28:48.760 --> 28:49.620
Don't touch me.

29:00.640 --> 29:01.800
Come down.

29:02.480 --> 29:03.240
Blockhead.

29:03.400 --> 29:04.040
Stop right there.

29:04.040 --> 29:05.600
Come catch me.

29:19.400 --> 29:20.130
Director Mu.

29:20.280 --> 29:21.360
So in your

29:21.360 --> 29:22.880
award-winning work this time,

29:22.880 --> 29:24.540
there is a girl named Yuanbao.

29:24.600 --> 29:25.880
In your previous work,

29:25.920 --> 29:27.800
there was also a girl named Yuanbao.

29:27.800 --> 29:29.440
So many netizens are curious.

29:29.440 --> 29:30.200
Is this Yuanbao

29:30.200 --> 29:31.920
the one you love?

29:32.080 --> 29:32.920
Would it be convenient

29:32.920 --> 29:34.120
to share with us

29:34.160 --> 29:35.080
your story?

29:35.200 --> 29:38.130
I have been looking for someone for nearly ten years.

29:38.400 --> 29:40.400
I want her to be the leading actress in my movie.

29:40.400 --> 29:43.200
I want to take her to Beijing to see the Bird's Nest.

29:43.240 --> 29:45.560
I want to take her to Tiananmen Square to watch the flag-raising ceremony.

29:45.560 --> 29:47.760
I want to spend the rest of my life with her.

29:47.760 --> 29:49.400
Her name is Yuanbao.

29:54.960 --> 29:56.520
That's so romantic!

29:56.800 --> 29:58.400
I believe countless female fans

29:58.400 --> 29:59.480
hearing such a story

29:59.480 --> 30:00.920
would be moved to tears.

30:01.240 --> 30:02.200
So at this moment,

30:02.200 --> 30:03.800
what do you want to say to her

30:03.880 --> 30:05.040
in front of the TV?

30:05.560 --> 30:09.000
The flower language of baby's breath is silent protection.

30:09.960 --> 30:12.440
I used to protect her silently.

30:13.240 --> 30:16.000
Now I want to continue to protect her.

30:24.040 --> 30:24.840
Yuanbao.

30:28.760 --> 30:29.880
Yaqi.

30:31.760 --> 30:32.480
Yuanbao,

30:32.760 --> 30:34.720
why didn't you come to the class reunion?

30:34.720 --> 30:36.320
Everyone misses you so much.

30:39.280 --> 30:40.840
Married Mu Qingjun.

30:41.560 --> 30:42.440
What are you talking about?

30:42.440 --> 30:43.520
Of course not.

30:44.200 --> 30:45.720
We are partners.

30:45.800 --> 30:47.000
Business partners.

30:49.600 --> 30:50.400
You know what?

30:50.720 --> 30:53.180
Actually, Qingjun has been looking for you.

30:55.320 --> 30:56.180
Looking for me?

30:57.800 --> 30:58.960
All these years,

30:59.480 --> 31:01.540
he has never given up looking for you.

33:22.080 --> 33:24.040
A long time ago, there was a little girl.

33:24.040 --> 33:26.960
Her tears could turn into sparkling diamonds,

33:27.120 --> 33:29.240
so people called her the Diamond Princess.

33:29.240 --> 33:29.920
Your tears

33:29.920 --> 33:32.250
have all turned into sparkling diamonds.

33:32.320 --> 33:34.600
This means you are also the Diamond Princess.

33:34.600 --> 33:36.280
You must keep this diamond safe.

33:36.280 --> 33:37.840
When you turn 18,

33:37.880 --> 33:38.960
we will come back here.

33:38.960 --> 33:39.880
Then we will know

33:39.880 --> 33:41.610
what gift the elf will give you.

33:43.000 --> 33:43.760
Miss,

33:44.120 --> 33:44.720
we have many customers coming here

33:44.720 --> 33:46.520
to customize diamond rings.

33:46.720 --> 33:48.520
But you are the first one

33:48.600 --> 33:50.160
to customize with broken glass.

33:50.160 --> 33:52.690
Presumably, this small piece of broken glass

33:52.720 --> 33:54.720
It must have a very special meaning.

33:58.400 --> 33:59.120
Yes.

33:59.280 --> 34:00.320
It was given to me

34:00.360 --> 34:02.280
by someone very important to me.

34:05.760 --> 34:07.400
You must come too.

34:08.159 --> 34:08.920
Definitely.

34:12.159 --> 34:15.760
If you were to act in 'A Chinese Odyssey' again,

34:17.320 --> 34:18.449
you play Zhi Zun Bao,

34:19.719 --> 34:20.920
and I play Zixia,

34:23.159 --> 34:24.440
would you still do it?

34:28.480 --> 34:29.639
Then that's it.

34:30.280 --> 34:31.940
The person I've been yearning

34:32.000 --> 34:34.760
and longing for is back.

34:35.199 --> 34:36.199
Then that's it.

34:37.000 --> 34:38.520
The person I've been yearning

34:38.520 --> 34:41.280
and longing for is back.

35:39.120 --> 35:40.440
Quick, make a wish!
